Notes: UMR outscores Oakland City 12-8 in the second overtime to pull out the win...
Deosha Agnew's lay-up with 4:17 to go put the Lady Miners up for good...OCU
tied the game at end of regulation (basket by Tanya Smith) and the first
overtime (basket by Jennifer Benson)...UMR plays at #2 Emporia State Dec. 30.
